{"words":[{"word":"oh","count":3},{"word":"heard","count":3},{"word":"new","count":3},{"word":"jingle","count":3},{"word":"beast","count":3},{"word":"lingyang","count":2},{"word":"yeah","count":2},{"word":"performance","count":2},{"word":"shop","count":2},{"word":"snack","count":2},{"word":"sounds","count":2},{"word":"meat","count":2},{"word":"hi","count":1},{"word":"boy","count":1},{"word":"brought","count":1},{"word":"liondance","count":1},{"word":"request","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"ton","count":1},{"word":"requests","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"fit","count":1},{"word":"mine","count":1},{"word":"lionpepper","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"waiting","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"lion","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"chow","count":1},{"word":"store","count":1},{"word":"opening","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"conflicts","count":1},{"word":"soldiers","count":1},{"word":"cancel","count":1},{"word":"nah","count":1},{"word":"worry","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"boyo","count":1},{"word":"focus","count":1},{"word":"big","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"looks","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"friend","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"came","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"monster","count":1},{"word":"wild","count":1},{"word":"recently","count":1},{"word":"call","count":1},{"word":"somehow","count":1},{"word":"nickname","count":1},{"word":"cute","count":1},{"word":"terrible","count":1},{"word":"stuff","count":1},{"word":"hunting","count":1},{"word":"makes","count":1},{"word":"jingling","count":1},{"word":"tusks","count":1},{"word":"half","count":1},{"word":"meter","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"claws","count":1},{"word":"shred","count":1},{"word":"prey","count":1},{"word":"ease","count":1},{"word":"actually","count":1},{"word":"ingredient","count":1},{"word":"messing","count":1},{"word":"things","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"anywhere","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"exile","count":1},{"word":"group","count":1},{"word":"called","count":1},{"word":"savages","count":1},{"word":"apparently","count":1},{"word":"cahoots","count":1},{"word":"sale","count":1},{"word":"crazy","count":1},{"word":"expensive","count":1},{"word":"five","count":1},{"word":"times","count":1},{"word":"usual","count":1},{"word":"price","count":1},{"word":"insane","count":1},{"word":"small","count":1},{"word":"supposed","count":1},{"word":"afford","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"snacks","count":1},{"word":"hand","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Oh hi! Isn't that the Lingyang boy?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"What brought you here? My liondance request? I heard you're getting a ton of requests. I hope you can still fit mine in.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Look, I got the Lionpepper and everything. Just waiting for you to put on the lion head and chow down at my store opening!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yeah, I heard. My thing conflicts with the performance you're doing for the soldiers, right? Will you have to cancel?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Nah, no need to worry about my little shop, boyo. Just focus on your big performance!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Oh, and you must be...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Haha, looks like Lingyang has made a new friend.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Here, try this while you're here! A new snack I just came up with!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Oh my, that'll be my great honor!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Have you heard? There's a monster in the wild recently, one they call the Jingle Beast...","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Yeah. Somehow the nickname sounds cute even!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But you know what? It does all the terrible stuff you can think of!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"When hunting, it makes these jingling sounds... They say its tusks are over half a meter long and its claws shred prey with ease.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Well, actually... I need this one ingredient for my new snack, but the Jingle Beast has been messing things up. Can't find good meat anywhere right now.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"There's only one place left to get it, and it's run by this Exile group called \"The Savages.\"","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"Apparently, they're in cahoots with the Jingle Beast, and that's how they still have meat for sale.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"But it's crazy expensive—five times the usual price! It's insane!","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"I'm just a small shop, how am I supposed to afford that?","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031},{"text":"So... I can't make a lot of these snacks for you to hand out yet.","quest_name":"Wild Heart's Return","quest_id":121000031}]}